    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J373">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I'm saying every day</l>
                    <l>"If I should be a Queen, tomorrow --</l>
                    <l>I'd do this way --</l>
                    <l>And so I deck, a litt[l]e,</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>If it be, I wake a Bourbon,</l>
                    <l>None on me, bend supercilious --</l>
                    <l>With "This was she --</l>
                    <l>Begged in the Market place --</l>
                    <l>Yesterday."</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Court is a stately place --</l>
                    <l>I've heard men say --</l>
                    <l>So I loop my apron, against the Majesty</l>
                    <l>With bright Pins of Buttercup --</l>
                    <l>That not too plain --</l>
                    <l>Rank -- overtake me --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And perch my Tongue</l>
                    <l>On Twigs of singing -- rather high --</l>
                    <l>But this, might be my brief Term</l>
                    <l>To qualify --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Put from my simple speech all plain word --</l>
                    <l>Take other accents, as such I heard</l>
                    <l>Though but for the Cricket -- just,</l>
                    <l>And but for the Bee</l>
                    <l>Not in all the Meadow --</l>
                    <l>One accost me --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Better to be ready --</l>
                    <l>Than did next morn</l>
                    <l>Meet me in Arragon --</l>
                    <l>My old Gown -- on --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And the surprised Air</l>
                    <l>Rustics -- wear --</l>
                    <l>Summoned -- unexpectedly --</l>
                    <l>To Exeter --</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
